snippet: Nigel Williams-Goss scored 15 points, and Washington held No. 13 San Diego State to a school record for fewest points in the Huskies' 49-36 win on Sunday....

headline.print_headline: Washington Knocks Off No. 13 San Diego State 49-36
headline.main: Washington Knocks Off No. 13 San Diego State 49-36

lead_paragraph: Nigel Williams-Goss scored 15 points, and Washington held No. 13 San Diego State to a school record for fewest points in the Huskies' 49-36 win on Sunday.
